{"tid":869073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(你的名字...) 小行星碎片掉大氣層  北海道天際大火球劃過函館百萬夜景","createTime":"2018-10-20T05:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T04:49:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c600d2c0282342697afcfe86c15b5f91dfd391a9","tid":869073,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"日本北海道上空昨天晚間出現一道神秘火光，因為很多人都看到了這團火球，網路上議論紛紛，是不是有外星人到訪？不過專家說應該是小行星或隕石，進入地球大氣層，摩擦產生的火光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sfrSxyDWkSDI79VrdI8Myg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/2f1212c37bfbda6d779550db225b3921\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsfrSxyDWkSDI79VrdI8Myg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F2f1212c37bfbda6d779550db225b3921&h=ddfc1a31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖／翻攝自北海道新聞 動画ニュースYouTube</span><br />\n<br />\n百萬函館夜景，美麗夜空突然竄出1顆火球，劃過天際後緩慢墜入地面或海面，台灣時間18號晚間7點56分，北海道各地攝影機都捕捉到這抹神秘火光。<br />\n<br />\n新聞主播：「銀河之森天文台表示，發光圓體看起來像是流星中特別明亮的，火球是數年一度才看得到的珍貴物體。」<br />\n<br />\n札幌、函館網友表示他們也看到了，在推特掀起熱議，但橫空出世的這顆火球，絕對不是外星人降臨。<br />\n<br />\n新聞主播：「應該是小行星進入大氣層，燃燒殆盡後變成流星後形成特別明亮的火球。」<br />\n<br />\n同樣是天外飛來的驚喜，愛知縣小牧市這戶民宅居民，感受像是在洗三溫暖．<br />\n<br />\n遭隕石砸屋居民：「以為是小偷從屋頂掉下來，一開始是這麼想。」<br />\n<br />\n這顆10公分大，重約550公克的隕石，9月26號晚間從天而降，直接把民宅屋頂砸破了一個洞．附近鄰居聽到「鏘」這樣的聲音，隕石下方還連著一塊磁石，最後經國立科學博物館鑑定後，判定是一塊擁有45億年歷史的隕石。<br />\n<br />\n東海TV岐阜聖德學園大學教授川上紳一：「砸到人有人死亡的事情是沒聽說，但有聽說過隕石砸到狗。」<br />\n<br />\n很多不同案例屋頂被這麼貴重的隕石給砸破，屋主不生氣，反倒樂壞了，日本博物館將它命名為「小牧隕石」，未來也將向國際隕石學會提出認證申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%93%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%8B%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E7%81%AB%E7%90%83-%E5%8A%83%E9%81%8E%E5%87%BD%E9%A4%A8%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%A4%9C%E6%99%AF-095944207.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%25A9%259A%25E8%25A6%258B%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A7%2598%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2590%2583-%25E5%258A%2583%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%2587%25BD%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25A4%259C%25E6%2599%25AF-095944207.html&d=do%2BRgQdsO12VW89BEKWd9LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=41519795\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%93%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%8B%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E7%81%AB%E7%90%83-%E5%8A%83%E9%81%8E%E5%87%BD%E9%A4%A8%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%A4%9C%E6%99%AF-095944207.html</a>"},{"pid":"ba56c5dbe4b1e3be502b4272bd15f25941ed1d7f","tid":869073,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7b04eff2dac7fd201dfb7b380b3594b4c79e3da","tid":869073,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:23:25.000Z","msg":"影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20181019/k10011677101000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fhtml%2F20181019%2Fk10011677101000.html&d=do%2BRgQdsO12VW89BEKWd9LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=fe76593b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20181019/k10011677101000.html</a>"},{"pid":"5ad278497ff2cd1d740156dcfd20cf7c7cecd568","tid":869073,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:30:45.000Z","msg":"20時54分札幌市内運転中に火球を目撃。ドラレコの映像とその拡大です。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kojik59/status/1052950694636937216/video/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkojik59%2Fstatus%2F1052950694636937216%2Fvideo%2F1&d=do%2BRgQdsO12VW89BEKWd9LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=46e342ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkojik59%2Fstatus%2F1052950694636937216%2Fvideo%2F1&h=caf8a6bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kojik59/status/1052950694636937216/video/1</a><br />\n&mdash; kojik59 (@kojik59) October 18, 2018"},{"pid":"fe90024c52d40b5163979a0cc8e1aa8fee1f3c3f","tid":869073,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b1811ace7830a652ff6dac1afba51a9048e47c","tid":869073,"uid":63952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"Your name"},{"pid":"dd9537b3e097a00728fe62b36e3e494353f3bd2f","tid":869073,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41780eadc6178e7605b2c0167ee596601f0c912e","tid":869073,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"10cm都可以咁光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12611716665986185b86b28578997a26c4730893","tid":869073,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:39:44.000Z","msg":"俾佢掟中真係難過中六合彩，不過會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecca83e096e23f17b68e84651814e826ce726c1","tid":869073,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41780eadc6178e7605b2c0167ee596601f0c912e","tid":869073,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"10cm都可以咁光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T20:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227848f78eae5f6e1433f7bad6ec65d3432138b4","tid":869073,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T20:16:34.000Z","msg":"你的名字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7731f05b91fc076b328798b80dd502b11979aa2","tid":869073,"uid":521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T20:16:46.000Z"